data.description: Located just west of Weiser out on the Flat, this incredible opportunity doesn't happen every day. This spacious, comfortable home has tons of natural light and great flow that just makes sense. With views for days and all the country peace and quiet you could ever wish for, you'll want to move on this. Sunsets over Indianhead Mtn, wildlife wandering through, fresh country air .. bring the family, livestock, toys - there's room for everything. Additionally, we are also offering the house and ten acres as well as a five-acre land only piece (with building permit!) Pasture is flood irrigated; high water table means very little to no irrigation required. There's also a 22x24 hay cover/shed/lean to for additional outdoor storage! Cherry, apple, peach, pear, plum trees! Sellers reserve the right to harvest the alfalfa (typically three cuttings).
